<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Sobre nós</h1> </div>

<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-00f7344 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="00f7344" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Desafiando o presente para construir o futuro.</h2> </div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8f6d055 dev-txt-w-medium elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8f6d055" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p>Somos a consultoria de negócios e tecnologia que mais cresce na América Latina, liderando transformações com tecnologia e soluções de que quebram barreiras e impulsionam resultados reais. Na Peers, acreditamos que o futuro não se espera, se constrói — com ousadia e parceira, ao lado dos nossos clientes. Estamos aqui para fazer as coisas de um jeito diferente.</p> </div>
</div>

const lazyloadRunObserver = () => {
const lazyloadBackgrounds = document.querySelectorAll( `.e-con.e-parent:not(.e-lazyloaded)` );
const lazyloadBackgroundObserver = new IntersectionObserver( ( entries ) => {
entries.forEach( ( entry ) => {
if ( entry.isIntersecting ) {
let lazyloadBackground = entry.target;
if( lazyloadBackground ) {
lazyloadBackground.classList.add( 'e-lazyloaded' );
}
lazyloadBackgroundObserver.unobserve( entry.target );
}
});
}, { rootMargin: '200px 0px 200px 0px' } );
lazyloadBackgrounds.forEach( ( lazyloadBackground ) => {
lazyloadBackgroundObserver.observe( lazyloadBackground );
} );
};
const events = [
'DOMContentLoaded',
'elementor/lazyload/observe',
];
events.forEach( ( event ) => {
document.addEventListener( event, lazyloadRunObserver );
} );
</script>
<script type="rocketlazyloadscript">(function () {
// Aplica em todos os forms CF7 dentro do widget UE/Elementor
document.querySelectorAll('.peers-form form.wpcf7-form').forEach(function (form) {
const q = (sel, ctx=form) => ctx.querySelector(sel);
const qA = (sel, ctx=form) => Array.from(ctx.querySelectorAll(sel));

const email = q('input[type="email"][name="email"]');
const phone = q('input[type="tel"][name="telefone"]');
const groupWrap = q('.wpcf7-form-control-wrap[data-name="forma_de_contato"]');
const checks = groupWrap ? qA('input[type="checkbox"]', groupWrap) : [];

// ---------- Helpers ----------
function ensureTipAfter(el) {
// cria/recupera um <span class="live-error"> logo após o field
let tip = el.nextElementSibling && el.nextElementSibling.classList && el.nextElementSibling.classList.contains('live-error')
? el.nextElementSibling
: null;
if (!tip) {
tip = document.createElement('span');
tip.className = 'live-error';
el.insertAdjacentElement('afterend', tip);
}
return tip;
}

// ---------- Validação: e-mail corporativo ----------
function validateCorporateEmail(showMsg) {
if (!email) return true;
const v = (email.value || '').trim().toLowerCase();
let ok = true, msg = '';

const m = v.match(/^[^\s@]+@([^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+)$/);
if (!m) {
ok = false; msg = 'Informe um e-mail válido.';
} else {
const domain = m[1];
const blocked = [
'gmail.com','googlemail.com',
'hotmail.com','hotmail.com.br',
'outlook.com','outlook.com.br',
'live.com','live.com.br',
'yahoo.com','yahoo.com.br',
'icloud.com','me.com',
'aol.com','gmx.com','ymail.com','mail.com',
'bol.com.br','uol.com.br','terra.com.br','msn.com',
'proton.me','protonmail.com','pm.me'
];
if (blocked.indexOf(domain) >= 0) {
ok = false; msg = 'Use e-mail corporativo (sem Gmail/Outlook/Hotmail/Yahoo etc.).';
}
}

const tip = ensureTipAfter(email);
if (!ok && showMsg) {
tip.textContent = msg;
tip.style.display = 'block';
email.classList.add('is-invalid');
} else if (!ok) {
email.classList.add('is-invalid');
} else {
email.classList.remove('is-invalid');
tip.textContent = '';
tip.style.display = 'none';
}
return ok;
}

// ---------- Máscara: telefone BR ----------
function maskPhone() {
if (!phone) return;
let v = (phone.value || '').replace(/\D/g, '');
if (v.startsWith('55') && v.length > 11) v = v.slice(2); // remove +55 se veio
if (v.length > 11) v = v.slice(0, 11);

if (v.length <= 2) {
v = v.replace(/^(\d{0,2}).*/, '($1');
} else if (v.length <= 6) {
v = v.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d+)/, '($1) $2');
} else if (v.length <= 10) {
v = v.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d{4})(\d+)/, '($1) $2-$3'); // fixo
} else {
v = v.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d{5})(\d{4}).*/, '($1) $2-$3'); // celular
}
phone.value = v;
}

// ---------- Validação: grupo de checkboxes (>= 1) ----------
function validateGroup(showMsg) {
if (!groupWrap) return true;
const ok = checks.some(cb => cb.checked);

let tip = groupWrap.querySelector('.live-error');
if (!ok && showMsg) {
if (!tip) {
tip = document.createElement('span');
tip.className = 'live-error';
groupWrap.appendChild(tip);
}
tip.textContent = 'Selecione ao menos uma opção.';
tip.style.display = 'block';
groupWrap.classList.add('is-invalid');
} else {
groupWrap.classList.remove('is-invalid');
if (tip) { tip.textContent = ''; tip.style.display = 'none'; }
}
return ok;
}

// ---------- Bindings ----------
if (phone) {
phone.addEventListener('input', maskPhone);
phone.addEventListener('blur', maskPhone);
}
if (email) {
email.addEventListener('input', () => validateCorporateEmail(false));
email.addEventListener('blur', () => validateCorporateEmail(true));
}
if (checks.length) {
checks.forEach(cb => cb.addEventListener('change', () => validateGroup(false)));
}

// Bloqueia envio se inválido (antes do Ajax do CF7)
form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
const okEmail = validateCorporateEmail(true);
const okGroup = validateGroup(true);
if (!(okEmail && okGroup)) e.preventDefault();
});

// Ajuste nos eventos do CF7 (fallback)
document.addEventListener('wpcf7invalid', () => { validateCorporateEmail(true); validateGroup(true); });
document.addEventListener('wpcf7reset', () => {
Array.from(form.querySelectorAll('.is-invalid')).forEach(el => el.classList.remove('is-invalid'));
const tipG = groupWrap && groupWrap.querySelector('.live-error'); if (tipG) tipG.remove();
if (email) {
const tipE = email.nextElementSibling && email.nextElementSibling.classList.contains('live-error') ? email.nextElementSibling : null;
if (tipE) tipE.remove();
}
});
});
})();

<script type="rocketlazyloadscript" data-rocket-type='text/javascript' id='unlimited-elements-scripts'>window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {

/* Content Carousel scripts: */

jQuery(document).ready(function(){
function uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87_start(){
var objCarousel = jQuery('#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87');
var objClonedItems;
var itemHolderSelector = '.uc_image_carousel_container_holder';
function equalizeContentHeight(){
var dataEqualHeight = objCarousel.data("equal-height");
if(dataEqualHeight == false)
return(false);
var objContents = objCarousel.find(".content-padding");
if(!objContents)
return(false);
var maxHeight = 0;
objContents.each(function(){
var objContent = jQuery(this);
var contentHeight = Math.round(objContent.outerHeight());
if(contentHeight > maxHeight)
maxHeight = contentHeight;
});
objContents.each(function(){
var objContent = jQuery(this);
objContent.css("min-height", maxHeight+"px");
});
}
function initCarousel(){
//cloned items fancybox fix
var objItems = objCarousel.find(itemHolderSelector);
var itemsNum = objItems.length;

//set data index for each origin item
for(let i=0; i<itemsNum; i++){

var objItem = objItems.eq(i);

objItem.attr('data-fancy-index', i);
}
objCarousel.owlCarousel({
loop: true,
rtl: false,
center:false,
autoplayTimeout : 5000,
autoplayHoverPause:true,
smartSpeed: 1000,
changeItemOnClick:false,
paddingType: 'none',
dots: true,
navText: ["<i class='fas fa-arrow-left'></i>","<i class='fas fa-arrow-right'></i>"],
nav: true,
autoplay: false,
margin: 20,
delayBeforeLoad: 0,
autoHeight: false,
mouseDrag:true,
touchDrag:true,
responsive : {
0 : {
items:1,

dotsEach: 1,
},
768 : {
items:2,

dotsEach: 1,
},
980 : {
items:3,

dotsEach: 1,
}
}
});
//wait while carousel init
setTimeout(function(){

var useFancybox = objCarousel.data("lightbox");

if(useFancybox == false)
return(false);

var imageLinkSelector = '.ue_img_link'; //link on image
//init fancybox only on non cloned items
var fancyLink = objCarousel.find(".owl-item:not(.cloned) "+imageLinkSelector);

fancyLink.attr("data-fancybox", "gallery")

fancyLink.fancybox({
loop: true,
arrows : true,
backfocus: false
});

//for cloned items find origin items and trigger it
objClonedItems = objCarousel.find(".owl-item.cloned");

objClonedItems.on('click', function() {

var objClonedItem = jQuery(this);
var objClonedItemChild = objClonedItem.find(itemHolderSelector);
var clickedDataFancyIndex = objClonedItemChild.data('fancy-index');
var objOriginItem = objCarousel.find('.owl-item:not(.cloned) [data-fancy-index='+clickedDataFancyIndex+'] '+imageLinkSelector);
var objOriginOwlItem = objOriginItem.parent('.owl-item');

objOriginItem.trigger('click');

//do nothing with clicked cloned item https://obu.edu/_resources/ldp/galleries/fancybox/
return(true);

});

},300);
//equalize height of content if needed
equalizeContentHeight();
setTimeout(function(){window.dispatchEvent(new Event('resize'));},200)
}
initCarousel();
objCarousel.on("uc_ajax_refreshed",function(){
objCarousel.trigger('destroy.owl.carousel');
initCarousel();
});
objCarousel.trigger("uc-object-ready");
jQuery(document).trigger("uc-remote-parent-init", [objCarousel]);

}if(jQuery("#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87").length) uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87_start(); else
jQuery( document ).on( 'elementor/popup/show', () => { if(jQuery("#uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87").length) uc_content_carousel_new_elementor_37afc87_start();});
});
